{"pin":"BH00454","subcodes":[{"code":"BH00454","anchor":"","title":"Lawh-i-Huriyyih (Tablet of the Maiden)","first_line":"Praise be unto Thee, O Lord, My God! I mention Thee at this moment when the Sun of Thy divinity is shining from the horizon of the Heaven","first_line_orig":"سبحانک اللهم یا الهی اذکرک حینئذ حین الذی استشرقت شمس الوهیتک عن افق سماء  ","language":"1","word_count":"1580","subjects":"@transcendence; unknowability of God, @symbolism, @expressions of grief; lamentation; sadness, @mystical themes","notes":" \u003ca href=\"https://d9263461.github.io/cl/Baha'i/Others/ROB/V1/Contents.html\"\u003eROB1.125\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"https://d9263461.github.io/cl/Baha'i/Others/ROB/V3/Contents.html\"\u003eROB3.223\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"http://bluefin.live/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/BKOG.pdf#page=23\"\u003eBKOG.167\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"https://bahai-library.com/bahailib/1504.pdf#page=223\"\u003eMMAH.211\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"https://reference.bahai.org/fa/t/o/GS/gs-20.html\"\u003eGSH.020\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070930181707/http://bahai-library.com/resources/leiden.list/leiden.list.html#118\"\u003eLL#118\u003c/a\u003e","translations":[{"language":"mi","lang_name":"Maori"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"ky","lang_name":"Kirghiz"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"sw","lang_name":"Swahili"},{"language":"uk","lang_name":"Ukrainian"},{"language":"ha","lang_name":"Hausa"}]}]}
